    "name": "凡加罗战术 Vangaro Tactics",
    "steam_appid": 2221530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《凡加罗战术》</strong>是一款色彩鲜艳的回合制策略游戏，在这里将领们有尖尖的鼻子，也有专门的隐秘任务。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将指挥一系列鲜活的卡通风格单位纵横战场，除了“正面交战”的关卡之外，还有需要在深夜潜入敌后的隐秘任务，你必须谨慎选择自己的行动才能避免一下子惊动太多敌人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/6459eb65dcad678890fa8e7118e84b2c.avif?t=1770983363\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/42a1cfd1307c9df785fcd03d1332f851.webp?t=1770983363\" width=617 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在凡加罗世界大战中与众多背景迥异、形象鲜明的各方指挥官们交手。从新人到老兵、从出身平凡到王亲国戚，每一位将领都对这场将他们卷入的战争有着不同的视角与看法。使用<strong>指挥官能力</strong>来扭转战局吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/c83fe6650fc865539b7c7273315faefb.poster.avif?t=1770983363\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/c83fe6650fc865539b7c7273315faefb.webm?t=1770983363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/c83fe6650fc865539b7c7273315faefb.mp4?t=1770983363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/b58519bfb0a082e93b5773490c373da6.webp?t=1770983363\" width=617 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>于深夜潜入敌后</strong>，执行隐秘任务。敌众我寡，因此你需要充分了解自己的军队、谨慎挑选进攻的目标，在他们有时间将敌袭警报传达给下一个哨站之前将敌人击溃。在众多任务中通过采矿挖掘和征召部队来智胜敌军，克服每一道难关。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/33c33676bb03d7cbcff727393b6f2151.poster.avif?t=1770983363\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/33c33676bb03d7cbcff727393b6f2151.webm?t=1770983363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/33c33676bb03d7cbcff727393b6f2151.mp4?t=1770983363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/f60f90cf44ba1c9053ca85a43e2ec217.webp?t=1770983363\" width=617 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将指挥色彩鲜艳的海陆空三军部队。让<strong>步兵</strong>占领建筑和开采资源，以<strong>载具</strong>来提供更强大的火力、运输和其他功能。没有哪一种单位完美无缺，即使是强大的坦克也有可能需要八方支援！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/9c8ad680ec7388c4f7ba93b64d3e885e.avif?t=1770983363\" width=600 height=105 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/de1534969632df1b5461344f31e17d1b.poster.avif?t=1770983363\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/de1534969632df1b5461344f31e17d1b.webm?t=1770983363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/de1534969632df1b5461344f31e17d1b.mp4?t=1770983363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/221165fc1344f77a6c09a1ab4ffb1b6d.webp?t=1770983363\" width=617 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过体验拥<strong>有专属单位的多个非对称</strong>阵营来领略凡加罗世界的一切。虽然每一阵营都共享一些通用单位，但各方都有属于自己的特殊单位，能够在不同的地形和场景下获取战术优势。根据不同阵营与指挥官来<strong>改变你的战术与玩法</strong>，试图找出最优策略，取得每场战斗的胜利。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/4411413395c7c4df4728acd827594cca.avif?t=1770983363\" width=616 height=209 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/bef2531786aa5e6a04edb51d04ae32b5.webp?t=1770983363\" width=617 height=61 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开采</strong>资源和<strong>占领</strong>工厂来获得收入，然后在兵营中征召新单位。占领的工厂可以每回合提供资源，但矿产是有限的，务必优先抢夺来占据优势！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/4cdc745a9dc3a062c79a8e9e21adbd04.poster.avif?t=1770983363\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/4cdc745a9dc3a062c79a8e9e21adbd04.webm?t=1770983363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/4cdc745a9dc3a062c79a8e9e21adbd04.mp4?t=1770983363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与众多个性鲜明且拥有改变战局能力的指挥官们交手 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在隐秘行动任务中夜袭敌后哨站 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥鲜艳的卡通风格海陆空三军部队 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精通拥有专属单位的多个非对称阵营 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >占领建筑和开采有限的资源来征召新部队 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从不同指挥官的视角体验凡加罗世界大战的进程 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221530/extras/75351452111075ebab0e64f4d1eb7568.avif?t=1770983363\" width=616 height=92 /></span></p>",
